Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/edmundlod/route-summarization
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: route-summarization
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, perl, libnet-cidr-lite-perl
Description: IP route summarization and CIDR aggregation tool
 Reads IPv4 and IPv6 networks one per line from stdin and outputs a
 summarized, aggregated list of CIDR blocks. Supports an optional --spf
 mode for parsing SPF prefix notation, as used by postallow.
